Because we had grown ambitious enough

03:49:38.720 --> 03:49:40.480
After making base camp for 20 years

03:49:40.480 --> 03:49:42.160
That we thought we could tackle that problem

03:49:42.160 --> 03:49:43.200
So I thought hey

03:49:43.840 --> 03:49:45.440
This is dumb

03:49:45.440 --> 03:49:48.240
